# Docker Setup

## Architecture
- Multi-stage build: Node.js 22 (build) → nginx alpine (production)
- Port 80 internal, 8080 external mapped
- nginx serves static files from `/usr/share/nginx/html`
- SPA routing configured via `try_files $uri /index.html`

## Commands
```bash
# Build and start
docker compose up --build

# Build only
docker build -t woped-next .

# Start container
docker run -p 8080:80 woped-next

# Show logs
docker compose logs -f
```

## Production Optimizations
- Gzip compression enabled
- Cache headers for static assets
- Security headers configured
- Health check on `/`
